QUESTIONS OR CONCERNS?

Write, call, or fax my Washington office about legislation before Congress:

Washington Office

2372 Rayburn House Office Building

Washington, DC 20515

phone: 202-225-1640

fax: 202-225-1641

Washington Office Hours:

Monday - Friday 8:30 a.m. EST to 6:00 p.m. EST

MAY I ASSIST YOU?

Write, call, or fax one of my Texas offices about problems with the Social Security Administration, Veterans Administration, Medicare, Federal Agencies or Passports:

District Office Hours:

Monday - Friday 8:00 a.m. CST to 5:30 p.m. CST

Laredo Office

602 E. Calton Road, Suite 2

Laredo, Texas 78041

phone: (956) 725-0639

fax: (956) 725-2647

Rio Grande City Office
